1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Sleeping in on weekends
is sabotaging your Monday.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
You think you're "catching up" on sleep. But
your body clock just shifted 2 hours.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
It's called social jetlag. Every 1 hour of weekend
shift = flying 1 timezone. You're jet-lagged every Monday.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Keep your wake time within 90
minutes of weekday. Saturday included.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
VOLT Sleep gives you 1 action per day
to fix this. Free. Link in bio.

